org.darkimport.omeglespy_z
Class LogHelper

java.lang.Object
  org.darkimport.omeglespy_z.LogHelper
Direct Known Subclasses:
DefaultLogHelper
public abstract class LogHelper
extends Object

This LogHelper is used throughout the core library for logging in lieu of establishing a dependency on a logging framework. The offshoot is that, unless you want this library's output logged to System.out, you must provide a concrete implementation of LogHelper that utilizes your logging framework of choice. If this class seems to be missing elements that would make it more convenient to use your desired logging framework, please fill out an issue at http://code.google.com/p/omeglespy-z/issues/list
